ent paint color in my apartment?<br> 	<b>B:</b> I have to see a sample. Bring me one this week, please.<br> 	<b>A:</b> How long will it take for my new apartment to be ready?<br> 	<b>B:</b> Both the new paint and new carpet will be finished by next week.<br>
